<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="regret-n">regret <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'ɡret/    美 /rɪ'ɡret/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>遗憾；悔恨：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>have</strong> no <strong>regrets about</strong> leaving. 
我毫不后悔离开。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Much to my regret</strong>, I am unable to accept your kind invitation.
非常遗憾，我不能接受你的盛情邀请。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is <strong>with great / deep regret</strong> that I accept your resignation.
接受你的辞呈，我感到非常遗憾。</p></div></div>